         <abstract>
            <p>Here we present a Riemann-Siegel integral formula for the Lerch zeta function. Proceeding as in Turing's method for computing the Riemann zeta function, our integral formula allows for the numerical computation of the Lerch zeta function by numerical quadratures.</p>
